OL,3,CThe young men in Cardiff fighting
OL,4,Chomelessness through mixed martial arts
OL,6,F"I've never felt better, I feel
OL,7,Fhealthier than I've ever been in my
OL,8,Flife."
OL,10,FMason says that he was bullied as a
OL,11,Fchild and never had a stable home,
OL,12,Fwhich could have left him choosing a
OL,13,Fvery different path in life.
OL,15,F"I lived my life very on the edge," he
OL,16,Fsaid. "I was doing what I wanted, not
OL,17,Fcaring for anything but myself, and
OL,18,Fthen when I got into martial arts it
OL,19,Fshowed me that you've got to show a
OL,20,Fcertain amount of discipline to get
OL,21,Fwhere you want to be."
