OL,3,CThe young men in Cardiff fighting
OL,4,Chomelessness through mixed martial arts
OL,6,FRobert Green, who runs the fighting
OL,7,Fhomelessness service, says Mason can
OL,8,Fbe an inspiration to other young
OL,9,Fpeople in his situation.
OL,11,FHe said: "He's the first one to break
OL,12,Fthe mould, so other young people will
OL,13,Fsee him and now know that it's
OL,14,Frealistic to achieve these kind of
OL,15,Fgoals."
OL,17,FMason's come away from his experiences
OL,18,Fwith one overwhelming feeling "The
OL,19,Fgrass ain't greener on the other side,
OL,20,Fit's greener where you grow it."
